A '''stinger''', or '''Iskalonian stinger''', was a powerful hand-held [[Blaster/Legends|blaster]] used by the [[Iskalonian|marine species]] on [[Iskalon/Legends|Iskalon]]. Built for use under water, it was much more powerful than a standard blaster, but had much shorter range.

